Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.95,0:00:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.33,0:00:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.62,0:00:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.17,0:00:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.74,0:00:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛苦..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.85,0:00:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾江同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.18,0:00:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 最近都不来部室 还以为你退部了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.11,0:00:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新谷同学请假之后第一次来这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.52,0:00:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小..小此木
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.33,0:00:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又..消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.90,0:02:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪之九 怨念少女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.13,0:02:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贞一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 夕子学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？遵命遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.17,0:02:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 贞一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎..怎么啦啊 夕子学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.21,0:02:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么呀 就是要紧紧抱着你而已呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高兴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.57,0:02:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？这..这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你喜欢我对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为..我喜欢夕子学姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.01,0:03:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说 那个是骗人的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..不是骗人的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就再说一次给我听
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.31,0:03:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次对我说你喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.50,0:03:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不出来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愿说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.44,0:03:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就说呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快~一~点~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是..是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.18,0:03:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再大声一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.35,0:03:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一口气！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对夕子学姐..！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.86,0:03:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾江同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在玩什么相声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么相声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正是要紧的时候 你不要来乱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.41,0:03:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子才是 一大早就挡着校门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:03:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是来乱的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.25,0:04:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还真是不觉得厌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三百六十五天都在那卿卿我我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.07,0:04:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不扯这些 新谷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于昨天的事..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.55,0:04:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走 贞一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊 夕子学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子..生气了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.43,0:04:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贞一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说贞一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你这样一声不应很无聊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正在考试
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是考试中哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.67,0:04:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关系大着了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.41,0:04:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 继续刚才那个话题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不说给我听的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.47,0:04:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就把试卷的答案说出来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:04:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以跑去看正确答案的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.12,0:05:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.33,0:05:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60}喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？只有这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs70}最喜欢你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 用嘴巴说出声来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.13,0:05:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后我们再慢慢说吧 贞一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想这样蒙混过关对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛痛..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:30.25,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}测验时间 40分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面的人 把答案纸收起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等..等一下！
